    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>* Time Products Inc., New York, to Favara, Skahan, Raffle, New York, to handle media duties for its Luxury Watch division, previously handled by Victor Norman &amp; Partners, New York. Billings were estimated at more than $1 million. In a separate review, Time Products kept Favara, Skahan as the agency handling the account of another division, Judith Leiber.</p>
      </block>
